  "recipe_notes": [
    "Reserve 1 tablespoon of cooking oil for saut\u00e9ing the aromatics (in addition to the 1/2 cup for frying).",
    "When flipping the stuffed eggplant, use two spatulas to prevent the filling from falling out.",
    "Ensure the eggplant is fully cooked and tender before peeling."
  ],
